    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its life. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission provides consistent shifting through all gears. On the exterior, the paint maintains a healthy gloss, though there are minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with all power features and electronics working properly, despite some light wear on the upholstery. It is a dependable vehicle that is ready for daily use without needing immediate major repairs.",
