    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of uncompromising care and meticulous maintenance. Mechanically superior and visually indistinguishable from new, this example is curated for the discerning enthusiast who demands absolute excellence.",
