    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's been meticulously cared for and looks brand new, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
