    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero paint imperfections or road rash. Inside, the cabin is in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of wear, creases, or fading. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the panoramic sunroof and advanced safety tech, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance and a ride quality that is both silent and powerful. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 48500.0,
